'''Eliey''' was one of the five redoubts built by the [[Sons and Daughters of Freedom|Freedom's Sons]] around the [[Intergalactic Communications Center]] during the [[Battle of Praesitlyn]]. Gunners at this fort could fire in any direction to protect [[Zozridor Slayke]]'s force's flank. It was taken by the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]] during the battle.

